    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crisis Wing</strong> combines the frantic, high-octane action of arcade classics with modern features and polished gameplay. Featuring authentic 16-bit visuals and a head-banging FM soundtrack, this is the vertical shoot 'em up you've been waiting for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 Intense Stages:</strong> Fight through a series of challenging levels, each with unique enemies and massive bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgradable Weapons:</strong> Power up your ship with three unique weapons and special sub-weapons to sow a wake of destruction in your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Co-op:</strong> Team up with a friend and double the firepower to tackle the game together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bonus Modes:</strong> Test your limits in the challenging Boss Rush and Score Attack modes, or perfect your run in Practice Mode with infinite lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Authentic Feel:</strong> Enable CRT filters for a truly old-school arcade experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready and blast off your thusters, the galaxy needs you!<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>App Version 1.2.2 </strong>- Dec 29, 2025</p>",
